long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Roblox Bookmarker is a free Google Chrome extension made by me (N_aps) that adds features to the Roblox.com website!

Some of the features included are:

- Add bookmarks from game pages
- Dark/Light mode
- Bookmarks displayed above all other games

Features in the works:

- Bookmark folders
- Notes for games

- N_aps
